---
import GlobalLayout from "../layouts/GlobalLayout.astro";
---

<GlobalLayout title="Financial Education" description="Articles and resources from Glorious Destiny Advisory—education first.">
  <section class="bg-ink text-ivory py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold">Financial Education</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-ivory/75 font-sans text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Short articles and concepts to nurture leads and reinforce authority—always educational, never hype.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="py-16 bg-ivory">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 font-sans text-muted text-center">
      <p>Phase 2: add Astro Content Collections for blog posts, or embed YouTube for a video library.</p>
      <p class="mt-8">
        <a href="/free-training" class="text-gold-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Start with free training →</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</GlobalLayout>
